hr.fer.zemris.java.tecaj.hw4.collections

Class SimpleHashtable.TableEntry

  • java.lang.Object
    • hr.fer.zemris.java.tecaj.hw4.collections.SimpleHashtable.TableEntry
  • Enclosing class:
    SimpleHashtable

    public static class SimpleHashtable.TableEntry
extends java.lang.Object
    This class is representation of an element in hash table. It has three properties: key, value and next as a reference to next hash table element in same slot.

    Implements getters for key and value, and setter for value. Overrides toString() method which returns key and value in format "key=value".

    Version:
    1.0
